Dia. 02 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's throw-in move at 1 is a \cf1\b brilliant move\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par If White plays at 2, Black wins the capturing race with 3.
\par However if White takes it with A instead of 2, Black still captures White with B.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
